summary: A unique memecoin in existence, an experiment in decentralized spontaneous community building. - BIBIToken is a purely community-driven organization that was built by the BIBIToken leaders, BIBIToken builders, and BIBIToken holders. BIBIToken is not just about crypto, but more about one kind of meme culture which is represented by BIBIERS, a group of brave and positive WEB3 new immigrants. By the Community For the Community
